Description:
CANNONEER: I was wondering if you had any thoughts?
EXILE: Plenty. 
CANNONEER: I mean about our current situation.
EXILE: It is unexpected. I never imagined my journey would lead down here, but my destination is the same.
CANNONEER: Pfft. I think you're excited!
EXILE: I am not. Well. Maybe a little.
Name: Overheard at Zee: Above or Below
